SuklaaMbaradharaM viShNuM SaSivarNaM caturbhujaM |
prasannavadanaM dhyaayEt sarvavighnOpaSaaMtayE ||

namOstE&stu tE vyaasa viSaalabuddhE phullaaraviMdaayatapatranEtra  |
Ena tvayaa bhaaratatailapoorNaH prajvaalitO j~jaanamayaH pradeepaH ||

naarayaNaM namaskRutya naraM caiva narOttamaM |
dEveeM sarasvateeM vyaasaM tatO jayamudeerayEt ||

vaMdE SaMbhumumaapatiM suraguruM vaMdE jagatkaaraNaM 
vaMdE pannagabhooShaNaM mRugadharaM vaMdE paSoonaaM patiM |
vaMdE sooryaSaSaaMkavahninayanaM vaMdE mukuMdapriyaM
